<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 15. Distribution map of Typhlocolenis. Double circle: Typhlocolenis sillaensis sp. nov. Square: T. jejudoensis sp. nov. Circle: T. fusca Hoshina. Star: T. uenoi Hoshina. Triangle: T. furunoi Hoshina." , "Figures 7 - 14. Typhlocolenis sillaensis sp. nov. (7, 8, 13). T. jejudoensis sp. nov. (9, 10, 14). T. fusca Hoshina (11). T. furunoi Hoshina (12) 7, 9, 11, 12 aedeagus, dorsal view 8, 10 ditto, lateral view 13, 14 spermatheca. Scale A: 0.2 mm (7 - 12). Scale B: 0.05 mm (13, 14)." , "Figures 1 - 6. Typhlocolenis sillaensis sp. nov. (1, 3, 6). T. jejudoensis sp. nov. (2, 4). T. uenoi Hoshina (5) 1, 2 habitus (paratypes) 3, 4 antenna 5, 6 elytral punctures. Scale A: 1 mm (1, 2). Scale B: 0.2 mm (3, 4). Scale C: 0.02 mm (5, 6)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/474264" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/474263" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/474262" .

